xmla Module

Defined in: src/Xmla.js:6705

This is xmla4js - a stand-alone, cross-browser javascript library for working with "XML for Analysis". XML for Analysis (XML/A) is a vendor-neutral industry-standard protocol for OLAP services over HTTP. xmla4js enables web-browser-based analytical business intelligence applications.
